@section{Summary}

Jimmy's explanation makes the most sense to me @emph{if} (and that's the
critical condition) we wish to truly improve the porches. If we merely wish
to improve the looks of our outdoor porches, any of the bids will
do. Indeed, we could just repair and repaint them. 




